Neither Scatterer nor EVE are updated for 1.9.1 last I checked.  Kopernicus likely not updated either (but I don't use it, so don't check it).  Unsure on the others in your list except TUFX (which requires KSP 1.9.x).

Need to either revert to KSP 1.8, or wait for those mods to update.
